                    <!--====== TOUR DESCRIPTION ==========-->
                    <div class="tour_head1">
                        <h3>Description</h3>
                        <p>The 133rd China Import and Export Fair is here! Popularly known as Canton Fair, this is one of the best trade fairs in the world. Get the chance to win more business opportunities, meet suppliers and hold one on one meetings in your area of interest. 

The fair has collaborated with nearly 3,500 high-quality enterprises in the clothing field, electronics, textiles and garments, office supplies, recreation products, medicines, medical devices and health products. 

Bonfire Adventures has successfully secured an excellent package giving you the chance to browse through the state-of-the-art exhibits, glimpse into the unique charm of the various folk customs, including outdoor excursions, dragon boat racing, and benefit with a great business turnover. 
</p>
                    </div>
